Package: modelminer
Type: Package
Title: Automated Model Selection with Feature Engineering
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Jesse", "Brandt",
      email = "jesse.a.brandt@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Automated forward model selection that searches over polynomial
    terms and interaction terms to find the formula that best optimizes a
    user-supplied metric (default: AIC). Supports greedy forward selection and
    forward-backward stepwise search. Works with any model function that accepts
    a formula and data argument, including lm, glm, and matrix-based models
    adapted via formula_wrap().
